Case1: Create with 1 Replica
- kubectl create -f file.yml
- kubectl get rs
- kubectl get pods
- kubectl describe pod <PN> & kubectl describe rs <RS-Name>

Case2: Increase the Replicas to 3 and apply
- vi file.yml and change replicas value to 3
- kubectl apply -f file.yml
- kubectl get rs
- kubectl get pods
- kubectl describe pod <PN> & kubectl describe rs <RS-Name>
